sub_title: Project officer AMR at Amsterdam UMC
summary: After completing a BSc at the Maastricht Science Programme in (Medical) Biology, I enrolled in a MSc in Healthcare Policy, Innovation and Management. Biology and other life sciences still interest me, but working in a laboratory was not what I wanted. Now I focus on improving processes in healthcare and looking for ways to help innovate or digitize the workplace.
